c0000000
00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:32.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Long-range magic
is a fickle thing</b></Default>

c0000001
00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:34.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and rather difficult to master.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:01:34.550 --> 00:01:37.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Success requires a combination
of three key factors</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:37.310 --> 00:01:38.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that are essential
to all mages.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:39.480 --> 00:01:40.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's the amount mana
utilized,</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:41.480 --> 00:01:42.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the strength
at which it's fired,</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:43.230 --> 00:01:45.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the level of control
you have over it.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:45.610 --> 00:01:46.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you know that much,
correct?</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:47.490 --> 00:01:48.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:01:48.820 --> 00:01:50.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Earlier,
your magic dissipated</b></Default>

c0000010
00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before it reached its target.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:01:52.190 --> 00:01:53.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That tells me
your levels of mana</b></Default>

c0000012
00:01:53.610 --> 00:01:55.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and your firing strength
are both lacking.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:01:56.410 --> 00:01:58.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These are not issues
that one can fix overnight.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:01:59.450 --> 00:02:00.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless of your talent,</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:01.120 --> 00:02:03.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>such skills will take years
to master.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:04.370 --> 00:02:05.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:08.260 --> 00:02:09.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That said...</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:09.460 --> 00:02:12.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the level of control you have
over your magic is very high.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:13.050 --> 00:02:15.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the area where
most people tend to struggle,</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:15.890 --> 00:02:18.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you're already exhibiting
great strength there.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:18.520 --> 00:02:20.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My advice is to be
patient with yourself.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:23.220 --> 00:02:24.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
All right.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:24.980 --> 00:02:27.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000024
00:03:31.170 --> 00:03:32.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000025
00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:36.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] Is Fern's
training coming along smoothly?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:37.550 --> 00:03:38.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a short four years,</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:38.930 --> 00:03:40.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she's learned more
than most do in ten.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:41.260 --> 00:03:42.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't feel this is
a good thing.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:43.050 --> 00:03:44.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is studying too hard.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:44.980 --> 00:03:48.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps. Nothing seems to
pull her out of the woods.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:51.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even so. I'm glad she's found
something she loves.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:51.770 --> 00:03:53.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless,
she's still a long way</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from becoming a proper mage.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:55.410 --> 00:03:56.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll have
deciphered the grimoire</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:56.780 --> 00:03:58.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before she reaches that status.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:59.410 --> 00:04:00.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that so?</b></Default>

c0000037
00:04:02.820 --> 00:04:03.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You know, Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:04:04.450 --> 00:04:06.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The odds this text contains
anything pertaining to--</b></Default>

c0000039
00:04:07.580 --> 00:04:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh?</b></Default>

c0000040
00:04:10.290 --> 00:04:11.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heiter?</b></Default>

c0000041
00:04:11.710 --> 00:04:14.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind howling]</b></Default>

c0000042
00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can wipe that look of pity
off your face.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:04:21.970 --> 00:04:23.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I consider the fact
I stayed on my feet</b></Default>

c0000044
00:04:24.050 --> 00:04:25.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for so long a minor miracle.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:32.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I will try to be
quick with my work.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, my friend.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:39.780 --> 00:04:41.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern, I need you with Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He collapsed.
Put your training on hold.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:46.370 --> 00:04:48.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] But I still haven't
shot through the boulder.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:49.790 --> 00:04:52.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no doubt you'll achieve
it eventually. Right now--</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:52.960 --> 00:04:54.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
It cannot be "eventually."</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:55.010 --> 00:04:56.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:57.300 --> 00:04:58.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
When "eventually" comes...</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:59.340 --> 00:05:01.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Master Heiter
will have passed away.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:05:04.470 --> 00:05:06.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That man saved my life,
you know.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:05:08.350 --> 00:05:11.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000057
00:05:17.030 --> 00:05:18.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000058
00:05:18.490 --> 00:05:20.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Throwing away your life now</b></Default>

c0000059
00:05:20.150 --> 00:05:21.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would be an utter waste.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:05:22.610 --> 00:05:23.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"A waste," Mister?</b></Default>

c0000061
00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A long time ago,
I lost someone, too.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:31.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was a dear companion
whom I cherished very much.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:35.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His heart was made of gold
and his nerves made of steel.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:05:35.260 --> 00:05:37.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He would sooner sacrifice
his life</b></Default>

c0000065
00:05:37.420 --> 00:05:39.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than abandon someone in need.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:41.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If he was still here,</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:42.130 --> 00:05:43.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I was the one
six feet below,</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:44.090 --> 00:05:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>more innocent lives
could've been saved.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:47.390 --> 00:05:49.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since I'm not the type
for such selflessness.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:50.060 --> 00:05:52.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I planned to live out
the rest of my days quietly,</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:53.310 --> 00:05:55.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but before
I could hole up for good,</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I realized something.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:57.400 --> 00:05:59.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I sat and died in silence,</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:59.780 --> 00:06:03.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all I learned about friendship,
strength of will, and courage.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:06:03.860 --> 00:06:06.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All the precious memories
we had made,</b></Default>

c0000076
00:06:06.500 --> 00:06:09.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they would vanish
like they had never been.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:06:09.700 --> 00:06:10.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:06:11.870 --> 00:06:14.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] If there is
even one precious memory</b></Default>

c0000079
00:06:14.250 --> 00:06:16.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>tucked within the walls
of your mind.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:06:17.300 --> 00:06:20.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I think it would be
a waste for you to die.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:06:22.550 --> 00:06:25.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Master Heiter fears
dying now more than ever</b></Default>

c0000082
00:06:25.390 --> 00:06:26.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because it means I'll be alone.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:06:28.640 --> 00:06:30.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to show him he did
the right thing back then.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:06:31.810 --> 00:06:33.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Saving my life can't be
his final regret.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:06:35.070 --> 00:06:37.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't care if it's as a mage
or whatever else,</b></Default>

c0000086
00:06:37.780 --> 00:06:39.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>learning some kind of skill
to support myself</b></Default>

c0000087
00:06:39.940 --> 00:06:41.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is my way of repaying him.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:06:42.440 --> 00:06:43.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's the reason I'm here</b></Default>

c0000089
00:06:44.190 --> 00:06:45.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I need him to know</b></Default>

c0000090
00:06:45.790 --> 00:06:47.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be all right
when he's gone.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Do you remember everything</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:52.370 --> 00:06:53.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I've taught you so far?</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:54.450 --> 00:06:56.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Yes.
-Good, then do as you like.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:07:00.050 --> 00:07:01.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000095
00:07:01.590 --> 00:07:04.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000096
00:07:41.500 --> 00:07:43.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000097
00:07:57.150 --> 00:07:58.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000098
00:07:58.520 --> 00:08:00.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There weren't any spells
for bringing back the dead</b></Default>

c0000099
00:08:00.690 --> 00:08:02.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or granting immortality.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:08:02.690 --> 00:08:03.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Worth the try.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:08:04.270 --> 00:08:05.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you know that?</b></Default>

c0000102
00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:09.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An immeasurable fear
of death lives within us all.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:08:09.490 --> 00:08:11.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If such spells did exist,</b></Default>

c0000104
00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:13.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ewig most surely would've
cast them on himself.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:08:14.490 --> 00:08:15.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then why bother?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:16.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000107
00:08:17.170 --> 00:08:19.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How's Fern?
Is she growing strong?</b></Default>

c0000108
00:08:19.960 --> 00:08:22.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She has room to improve
in some areas.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:08:22.330 --> 00:08:25.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it wouldn't be incorrect
to call her a proper mage.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:08:25.430 --> 00:08:26.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000111
00:08:27.260 --> 00:08:29.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excellent.
So, she made it in time.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:08:30.140 --> 00:08:31.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000113
00:08:31.390 --> 00:08:33.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be hard for you to say
she'll get in your way,</b></Default>

c0000114
00:08:33.930 --> 00:08:34.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>now won't it?</b></Default>

c0000115
00:08:35.690 --> 00:08:36.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000116
00:08:37.150 --> 00:08:39.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will you bring her with you
and strengthen her skills?</b></Default>

c0000117
00:08:40.730 --> 00:08:41.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Forgive me, Heiter,</b></Default>

c0000118
00:08:42.150 --> 00:08:43.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I must draw a line.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:08:44.560 --> 00:08:46.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She would only get in my way.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:08:46.990 --> 00:08:48.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've deceived me, didn't you?</b></Default>

c0000121
00:08:48.820 --> 00:08:51.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:55.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your payment for decrypting
the grimoire is in the desk.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:08:56.330 --> 00:08:58.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must ask you leave
this place tonight.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:08:59.420 --> 00:09:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For what reason?</b></Default>

c0000125
00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure you can see</b></Default>

c0000126
00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:05.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I am not much longer
for this world.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:09:06.180 --> 00:09:07.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At such a young age,</b></Default>

c0000128
00:09:07.550 --> 00:09:09.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that child
has already experienced</b></Default>

c0000129
00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>more than enough loss</b></Default>

c0000130
00:09:10.970 --> 00:09:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to last the rest
of her lifetime.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:09:13.970 --> 00:09:14.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:17.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please take care of Fern
for me.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:09:19.890 --> 00:09:21.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No point
in feigning courage again.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:09:21.980 --> 00:09:23.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Not now.
-Ah.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:09:25.740 --> 00:09:27.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] She has been ready
to say goodbye</b></Default>

c0000136
00:09:27.400 --> 00:09:28.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to you for a long while.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:09:29.740 --> 00:09:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your only focus before you die</b></Default>

c0000138
00:09:32.650 --> 00:09:34.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be giving her
a proper farewell.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:09:35.830 --> 00:09:37.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And making as many memories
as you can.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:09:38.540 --> 00:09:39.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffles]</b></Default>

c0000141
00:09:39.710 --> 00:09:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000142
00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Oh, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:09:44.370 --> 00:09:46.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really are a kind girl.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:09:47.720 --> 00:09:50.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000145
00:09:56.680 --> 00:09:59.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
So...why did you save Fern?</b></Default>

c0000146
00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:02.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathes]</b></Default>

c0000147
00:10:04.350 --> 00:10:07.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000148
00:10:16.290 --> 00:10:17.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Because that is what</b></Default>

c0000149
00:10:17.660 --> 00:10:19.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel the Hero would've done.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:21.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000151
00:10:22.580 --> 00:10:23.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You're right.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:10:36.770 --> 00:10:38.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A good guiding voice.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:10:39.640 --> 00:10:40.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps I'll listen as well.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:10:43.270 --> 00:10:46.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[church bells ringing]</b></Default>

c0000155
00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:53.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really
can't thank you enough.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:10:53.900 --> 00:10:55.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Without your help and guidance,</b></Default>

c0000157
00:10:55.830 --> 00:10:58.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't have repaid
Master Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:10:59.290 --> 00:11:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you should be
thanking him for deceiving me.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:11:03.330 --> 00:11:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So long, corrupt priest.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:12.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, shall we be off?</b></Default>

c0000161
00:11:26.770 --> 00:11:29.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000162
00:11:34.820 --> 00:11:35.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Stop there, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:11:36.450 --> 00:11:37.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's plenty.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:11:41.370 --> 00:11:43.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE FARMER 2A]
Thank you kindly for your help.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:11:43.530 --> 00:11:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As for your payment, take this.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:11:47.790 --> 00:11:50.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've been doing
such simple work lately.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:11:50.420 --> 00:11:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thus is the nature
of adventuring.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:54.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What did we get paid
in this time?</b></Default>

c0000169
00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:56.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
More folk magic.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:11:56.390 --> 00:11:58.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a spell that produces
warm tea.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:11:58.680 --> 00:12:00.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll have to
try this out later.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:12:00.470 --> 00:12:01.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000173
00:12:01.970 --> 00:12:03.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] The other day
we learned a spell</b></Default>

c0000174
00:12:03.390 --> 00:12:05.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that cleans rust
from bronze statues.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:12:06.230 --> 00:12:07.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And before that
there was the one</b></Default>

c0000176
00:12:07.770 --> 00:12:09.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-for turning sweet grapes sour.
-Sour?</b></Default>

c0000177
00:12:09.560 --> 00:12:10.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-huh.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:13.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You keep collecting
the strangest spells.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:12:13.980 --> 00:12:15.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That is my hobby.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:12:15.870 --> 00:12:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It sounds to me like</b></Default>

c0000181
00:12:17.030 --> 00:12:19.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you really do love magic,
Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:12:19.620 --> 00:12:21.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Only somewhat.
The same as you.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:12:23.070 --> 00:12:25.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I, uh,
feel we're a bit different.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:12:27.130 --> 00:12:28.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
We're the same.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:12:29.710 --> 00:12:30.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE HERBALIST 1A]
You're absolutely sure</b></Default>

c0000186
00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you wouldn't mind
doing me a favor?</b></Default>

c0000187
00:12:33.750 --> 00:12:34.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As an herbalist,</b></Default>

c0000188
00:12:35.130 --> 00:12:38.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say I have any spells
to teach you in return.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:12:39.090 --> 00:12:40.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's all right.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:12:40.470 --> 00:12:41.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any information we can learn</b></Default>

c0000191
00:12:41.890 --> 00:12:43.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on local flora
is helpful enough.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:12:48.310 --> 00:12:49.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE HERBALIST 1A]
There he is.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:12:54.810 --> 00:12:56.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
A statue of Himmel the Hero.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:12:57.320 --> 00:12:59.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HERBALIST 1A] The poor boy
is in terrible shape.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:13:00.110 --> 00:13:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would clean him myself,</b></Default>

c0000196
00:13:01.780 --> 00:13:03.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it's too much
for one old lady.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:07.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I can't convince
the other villagers to care.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:13:07.540 --> 00:13:10.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shouting indistinctly]</b></Default>

c0000199
00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

c0000200
00:13:16.260 --> 00:13:18.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[growls]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000201
00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:19.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000202
00:13:20.220 --> 00:13:22.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[growls]
-Huh!</b></Default>

c0000203
00:13:22.630 --> 00:13:24.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE HERBALIST 1A]
No!</b></Default>

c0000204
00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:31.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE HERBALIST 1A]
When the village was attacked</b></Default>

c0000205
00:13:31.770 --> 00:13:32.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by a vicious monster,</b></Default>

c0000206
00:13:33.020 --> 00:13:34.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the brave Mister Himmel</b></Default>

c0000207
00:13:34.390 --> 00:13:36.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fought with all his might
to defend us.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:13:37.070 --> 00:13:39.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Such a hero should be revered,
not left to crumble.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:13:41.110 --> 00:13:44.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps,
but not in Himmel's case.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:13:44.610 --> 00:13:46.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's only fair
that he pays for his pride.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:13:47.660 --> 00:13:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When the villagers offered
to make a statue of him,</b></Default>

c0000212
00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:51.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he should have humbly declined.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:13:52.370 --> 00:13:54.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[snoring]
-[HIMMEL] How is this?</b></Default>

c0000214
00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:56.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't think
it's too handsome, right?</b></Default>

c0000215
00:13:56.840 --> 00:13:59.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] He spent
18 hours choosing a pose,</b></Default>

c0000216
00:13:59.670 --> 00:14:01.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>driving the poor sculptor mad.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:14:02.300 --> 00:14:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of that debate</b></Default>

c0000218
00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:06.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and they settled on something
ridiculously ordinary.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:14:07.640 --> 00:14:09.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
I've never heard that before.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:14:09.770 --> 00:14:11.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come to think of it,</b></Default>

c0000221
00:14:11.180 --> 00:14:14.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there was an elven mage
in the hero's party,</b></Default>

c0000222
00:14:14.430 --> 00:14:15.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wasn't there?</b></Default>

c0000223
00:14:16.820 --> 00:14:18.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, shall we clean him up?</b></Default>

c0000224
00:14:18.900 --> 00:14:21.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[owl hooting]</b></Default>

c0000225
00:14:22.780 --> 00:14:24.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE HERBALIST 1A]
Thank you so much.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:14:24.860 --> 00:14:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Magic is an incredible thing.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:14:27.080 --> 00:14:29.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There isn't a speck of rust
anywhere in sight.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:14:29.910 --> 00:14:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000229
00:14:31.830 --> 00:14:34.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do wish there was a bit more
color around here, though.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:14:34.870 --> 00:14:36.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll have to plant
some flowers soon.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:14:37.550 --> 00:14:38.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We could do that.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:41.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have a spell that
produces flowers, don't you?</b></Default>

c0000233
00:14:41.710 --> 00:14:42.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, indeed.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:14:42.880 --> 00:14:44.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose
I could conjure something.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:14:48.180 --> 00:14:51.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, blue moon weed flowers
would be best.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:14:51.560 --> 00:14:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't recall that one,
what do they look like?</b></Default>

c0000237
00:14:54.060 --> 00:14:56.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I don't know.
I've never seen them.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:14:56.610 --> 00:14:57.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then why those?</b></Default>

c0000239
00:14:58.230 --> 00:15:00.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because they grow
in Himmel's hometown.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:15:00.820 --> 00:15:03.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't conjure flowers
you haven't seen before.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:15:04.230 --> 00:15:05.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:15:06.160 --> 00:15:07.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000243
00:15:07.870 --> 00:15:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000244
00:15:10.370 --> 00:15:11.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE HERBALIST 1A]
Blue moon weed.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:14.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Haven't heard that name
in years.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:15:16.840 --> 00:15:17.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Long ago,</b></Default>

c0000247
00:15:18.210 --> 00:15:19.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a beautiful, lush field of them</b></Default>

c0000248
00:15:19.840 --> 00:15:21.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>used to bloom
right outside my house.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:15:27.680 --> 00:15:29.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So,
they don't grow here anymore?</b></Default>

c0000250
00:15:30.720 --> 00:15:32.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems they died off on us.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:15:33.140 --> 00:15:34.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been several decades now</b></Default>

c0000252
00:15:34.720 --> 00:15:37.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since they were last spotted
in these lands.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:15:38.520 --> 00:15:39.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:15:42.730 --> 00:15:44.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern. Let's go.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:15:44.860 --> 00:15:45.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Coming.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:51.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You're hiding something.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:15:52.830 --> 00:15:54.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever it is,
I won't be upset.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:15:58.880 --> 00:16:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Found friends, did you?</b></Default>

c0000259
00:16:00.630 --> 00:16:02.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe they're seed rats.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:16:02.750 --> 00:16:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take them outside.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:16:09.140 --> 00:16:10.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Fern?</b></Default>

c0000262
00:16:10.390 --> 00:16:12.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shall our moon weed quest
commence?</b></Default>

c0000263
00:16:12.600 --> 00:16:14.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you joking, Mistress?</b></Default>

c0000264
00:16:14.930 --> 00:16:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would I be?</b></Default>

c0000265
00:16:16.150 --> 00:16:17.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said there was
a field of them right here.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:16:17.940 --> 00:16:19.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Decades ago.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:16:19.480 --> 00:16:21.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] But they're
well worth looking for.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:16:22.610 --> 00:16:24.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we're able to find
and analyze them.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:16:25.310 --> 00:16:27.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can conjure blue mood weed
wherever we like.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:16:29.070 --> 00:16:30.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're doing this
for Himmel's sake?</b></Default>

c0000271
00:16:31.490 --> 00:16:32.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:16:32.820 --> 00:16:34.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe I'm doing it
for my own.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:16:35.790 --> 00:16:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000274
00:17:27.760 --> 00:17:28.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:17:29.300 --> 00:17:31.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've scoured these woods
for six months.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:17:31.630 --> 00:17:33.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think
we're going to find it.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:17:33.800 --> 00:17:34.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You're right.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:17:34.880 --> 00:17:37.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps it's time we broaden
the radius of our quest.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:17:37.810 --> 00:17:38.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:17:41.350 --> 00:17:42.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knock on door]</b></Default>

c0000281
00:17:46.860 --> 00:17:47.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:17:48.280 --> 00:17:50.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't often see you
on your own.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:17:52.990 --> 00:17:54.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been quite a while</b></Default>

c0000284
00:17:54.150 --> 00:17:56.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since you two first arrived
in this village.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:17:57.960 --> 00:18:00.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, have you found
any blue moon weed?</b></Default>

c0000286
00:18:01.370 --> 00:18:03.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Is our search a lost cause?</b></Default>

c0000287
00:18:03.460 --> 00:18:04.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000288
00:18:05.290 --> 00:18:08.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's so quick to fixate
on anything relating to magic.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:18:09.630 --> 00:18:10.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the looks of it,</b></Default>

c0000290
00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:12.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she's going continue
this hunt for years,</b></Default>

c0000291
00:18:12.840 --> 00:18:13.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if not decades.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:18:15.050 --> 00:18:16.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Given her strength as a mage,</b></Default>

c0000293
00:18:16.390 --> 00:18:18.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she has the power to save
whole cities of people.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:18:20.480 --> 00:18:23.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She shouldn't spend her time
looking for something so tiny.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:18:23.730 --> 00:18:25.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something that may not exist.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:18:27.030 --> 00:18:28.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're so young, child.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:18:30.240 --> 00:18:31.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that simply
a polite way of saying</b></Default>

c0000298
00:18:32.070 --> 00:18:33.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you think I'm wrong?</b></Default>

c0000299
00:18:34.070 --> 00:18:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE HERBALIST 1A] No,
and I don't disagree with you.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:18:37.330 --> 00:18:38.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you see Miss Frieren</b></Default>

c0000301
00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>likely views things differently
than you and me.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:18:44.370 --> 00:18:46.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And because she's so much
more mature than us,</b></Default>

c0000303
00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:49.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure she'd understand
your feelings.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:18:49.630 --> 00:18:51.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you say how you feel
with an open heart.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:18:51.960 --> 00:18:53.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've no doubt
she'll take it well.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:18:55.970 --> 00:18:58.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000307
00:19:12.820 --> 00:19:14.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] They're the seeds
of a related species</b></Default>

c0000308
00:19:14.690 --> 00:19:16.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she kept
for their medicinal properties.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:19:17.790 --> 00:19:19.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would it be all right
if we planted these</b></Default>

c0000310
00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:21.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>around Himmel's statue instead?</b></Default>

c0000311
00:19:22.410 --> 00:19:23.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hear you, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:19:24.620 --> 00:19:26.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I see I've made you worry.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:19:27.590 --> 00:19:28.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:19:29.670 --> 00:19:32.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The time I spend isn't solely
my own anymore.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:19:32.920 --> 00:19:33.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should go.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:36.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise
that I'll end my search soon.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:19:37.260 --> 00:19:38.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmph?</b></Default>

c0000318
00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:42.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Mistress?
How many years is soon?</b></Default>

c0000319
00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:43.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, soon enough.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:19:44.970 --> 00:19:47.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, no.
That's not comforting coming--</b></Default>

c0000321
00:19:47.150 --> 00:19:48.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shh!</b></Default>

c0000322
00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:52.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000323
00:19:53.190 --> 00:19:54.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000324
00:19:59.030 --> 00:20:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shall we see
where it's heading?</b></Default>

c0000325
00:20:24.930 --> 00:20:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Fern groans]</b></Default>

c0000326
00:20:30.940 --> 00:20:32.360 line:90% align:center
